=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca50627296cdafa22e0068f4738fa9ac981a7bc2","tid":1219341,"uid":20058,"like":125,"dislike":1,"score":124,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T19:31:06.000Z","msg":"《逃犯條例》修訂爭議繼續升溫，近日更相繼有學生聯署發起罷課行動。昨日（12日）金鐘立法會一帶示威者與警方發生衝突後，教協宣布全港罷課，教育局局長楊潤雄今日（13日）傍晚致函全港學校的校長及校監，題為《緊守崗位　守護學生》，表明教育局堅決反對教育團體罷課及罷教；同時若有教師未經批准而缺席，學校應按照相關資助條例、僱傭條例及校本政策處理。<br />\n教育局正在和學校緊密聯絡，並了解學生缺席和教師人手調配的情況，稱以便提供適切支援。"},{"pid":"a6318d160ba4c579124de25057017c6b8bb7e493","tid":1219341,"uid":20058,"like":47,"dislike":1,"score":46,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T19:31:25.000Z","msg":"函件附政府修訂《逃犯條例》小冊子<br />\n<br />\n針對最近有教育團體發動罷課及罷教活動，教育局堅決反對，並指學校是學生學習的地方，任何人都不應以學校作為表達政治訴求的場地。<br />\n<br />\n函件續指，教師在任何情況下均須履行職責，緊守工作崗位，行為亦需要符合專業操守。教育局稱，學校作為僱主，有責任管理員工及監察他們的工作表現；若個別教師在工作時間未經學校批准而缺席，或沒有履行職務，學校須明確指出有關行為實屬不當，並應當按相關資助則例、僱傭條例及校本政策處理。<br />\n<br />\n信函中並附有保安局關於政府修訂《逃犯條例》的小冊子，但又指香港是一個多元社會，尊重不同意見，但老師應該引導學生多角度思考，以和平、合法方式表達意見。"},{"pid":"37cf509a05001a69f2cce2a42a9fc2b07543e6dc","tid":1219341,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T19:35:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"425bb8ea33db0b19193f89552d1a9411f57a2347","tid":1219341,"uid":20058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T19:36:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ffe8b2223c9ceeaebf75e2657ff74f97f1118cc","tid":1219341,"uid":258870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T19:38:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"445da9b510bc4a4cdc9d99198715334b51cf8c1c","tid":1219341,"uid":254192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T19:38:46.000Z","msg":"pish<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca814f66863aeecef305afff5203ddf78776dc4f","tid":1219341,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T19:39:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c83b31894f6cdc6c9cf7470de76974db71e4f857","tid":1219341,"uid":147888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T19:40:03.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"227254c7d92bfcb123492d1958cec98e5b0b43e6","tid":1219341,"uid":20058,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T19:40:50.000Z","msg":"熱狗系垃圾fb page look7 依家仲掛住搞白鴿<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1219234\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1219234</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n已經開始有人內鬥"},{"pid":"4cb17c95def100665594c73f2b5f14f301cb0235","tid":1219341,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T19:43:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji