36d9c8101ca738682b087f13","tid":1219341,"uid":231040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T06:44:52.000Z","msg":"[反送中] 《撐港共商戶及老闆》舉報中心<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1221024\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1221024</a>"},{"pid":"7fed3c2eb73979217361d626324b75170d9e0349","tid":1219341,"uid":68541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T06:46:06.000Z","msg":"賤到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}